snippet.title: Thin Ice (Nitrome.com) - Full Gameplay Levels 1-20
snippet.description:
Full gameplay of Thin Ice. A game from Nitrome.com about the hiker of Frost Bite, that this time has to skate in a frozen lake and make the enemies fall to the water by breaking the ice with his skates.
I hope you like it!
